<p><b>Slang names</b></p>
<p>Pointing stick devices are sometimes informally referred to as a "<a href="/wiki/Nipple" title="Nipple">nipple</a>" mouse<sup id="cite_ref-11" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-11" title=""><span>[</span>12<span>]</span></a></sup><sup id="cite_ref-12" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-12" title=""><span>[</span>13<span>]</span></a></sup>, "clit mouse"<sup id="cite_ref-13" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-13" title=""><span>[</span>14<span>]</span></a></sup><sup id="cite_ref-xkcd_14-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-xkcd-14" title=""><span>[</span>15<span>]</span></a></sup>, or "nub"<sup id="cite_ref-xkcd_14-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-xkcd-14" title=""><span>[</span>15<span>]</span></a></sup>.</p>
